/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放耐啲 2hrs會好啲<br />\n<br />\n大火封面 轉中火<br />\n大火再封另一邊 轉中火<br />\n<br />\nMedium well既做法<br />\n<br />\n想食medium就中大火<br />\n唔洗下下都用最大火既"},{"pid":"9fb71edad44ff24fe2e6d14d19aca64ce4a95c18","tid":247981,"uid":111019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:41:34.000Z","msg":"巴士用咩鑊煎我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我用陶瓷鑊煎係100%燶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n易潔鑊好似好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋應該隻鑊幾熱時落塊牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914de04dd26d80f4d56da0e3e9dec0eea549fe1f","tid":247981,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:43:16.000Z","msg":"厚既大火封完兩邊可以轉中火"},{"pid":"98f7445553ce170762b863bedfe43cecf140dad3","tid":247981,"uid":3208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:44:03.000Z","msg":"唔好用鑊 要用pan 受熱平均好多的  同埋解涷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先調味<br />\n<br />\n熱Pan熱油轉中火煎個邊先 碌2分鐘<br />\n<br />\n心入面計時  煎幾耐出水就反轉，另一面一樣時間<br />\n<br />\n最後開返大火煎脆個面 正常每邊一分鐘內都夠"},{"pid":"5ebcd8fc2784f2793ae914499d01f153d74de320","tid":247981,"uid":31178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:44:51.000Z","msg":"我見ramsay多數都係煎完之後入焗爐，一係就焗左先最尾煎一煎。"},{"pid":"495e216ce4137041c6246ab873829f85c13b309e","tid":247981,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴士用咩鑊煎我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我用陶瓷鑊煎係100%燶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n易潔鑊好似好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋應該隻鑊幾熱時落塊牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/