>\n大火不等於下下扭到最大。而且都睇你隻咩鑊。<br />\n不鏽鋼pan 要預熱比較耐（我隻要4分鐘），但係熱咗就唔使好大火 keep 溫度。<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得燶得快，下次扭細少少。底面各煎1-1.5分鐘攞顏色，再收細火，視乎想幾熟同厚度，再底面各煎2、3分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n如果火夠細，基本上可以無限煎而唔燶。"},{"pid":"865fd8da30fe7099bb483752ae98c638b295fa8a","tid":247981,"uid":36054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:13:58.000Z","msg":"新鮮牛扒要攤一攤 解凍先 <br />\n急凍既唔洗<br />\n鑊要預熱<br />\n<br />\n落肥膏/牛油 開鑊 <br />\n落扒 中火 每邊90秒<br />\n靜置5分鐘<br />\n<br />\n再落小小牛油 每邊30秒<br />\n用匙仔淋啲牛油上面 <br />\n<br />\n我就通常係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10554d2aee4fdce9526511f1acad4dd52f79d804","tid":247981,"uid":12498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:15:19.000Z","msg":"厚嘅就咁煎一定噥，澳洲佬叫個d做lovely brown<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生<br />\n1inch, 每邊大火兩分鐘，插支溫度計，啪入250c焗爐，等到120f, 攞出嚟rest 10min."},{"pid":"8b9b47843a29ce19ccf881b9dcd669408f3f4f98","tid":247981,"uid":50613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:19:14.000Z","msg":"salt and pepper<br />\nolive oil in the pan<br />\nsteak, in<br />\nthyme, garlic<br />\na minute each side<br />\nflip once<br />\nbutter, in<br />\nget a spoon, start basting"},{"pid":"5a1aac5811e6af34928049881c8b2d8ab1a41304","tid":247981,"uid":12070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:19:19.000Z","msg":"U u u u u get out"},{"pid":"a7f25053b2b3e6e52429c763dfb3657fde80f72c","tid":247981,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:20:54.000Z","msg":"太大火"},{"pid":"44628caf10f98433dd042c2123d28170b7e364a4","tid":247981,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:21:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1分鐘濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未到全燶 太係黑過睇片個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拍片個陣打左燈o者<img src=\"