"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:11:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收細火? 件野唔洗要</blockquote><br />\n應係大火煮到油出煙＞收中火＞落扒每面2分鍾＞夾起放10分鐘＞落牛油每面30秒＞食得"},{"pid":"a67c62361442397dc3f80a9829ee212bf003ca1e","tid":247981,"uid":92,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:12:33.000Z","msg":"煎完切左個面"},{"pid":"09da1d430371940b6302a763700a4eb107258304","tid":247981,"uid":111019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:16:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/180307_a005bc6c213fc462e5c31da52395b697.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F180307_a005bc6c213fc462e5c31da52395b697.jpg&h=3c39e32f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/180308_a005bc6c213fc462e5c31da52395b697.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F180308_a005bc6c213fc462e5c31da52395b697.jpg&h=e4b48687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係唔係太大火或者落得太多黑椒？</blockquote><br />\n幾好啊冇乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ccf72da1acfec0f98604f7062400991ebc12c0","tid":247981,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:23:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/180307_a005bc6c213fc462e5c31da52395b697.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F180307_a005bc6c213fc462e5c31da52395b697.jpg&h=3c39e32f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/180308_a005bc6c213fc462e5c31da52395b697.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F180308_a005bc6c213fc462e5c31da52395b697.jpg&h=e4b48687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係唔係太大火或者落得太多黑椒？</blockquote><br />\n幾好啊冇乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你依家靚好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7175b161c25f148499f73f6bc0a87b686a0390d0","tid":247981,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/180307_a005bc6c213fc462e5c31da52395b697.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F180307_a005bc6c213fc462e5c31da52395b697.jpg&h=3c39e32f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/18/180308_a005bc6c213fc462e5c31da52395b697.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F18%2F180308_a005bc6c213fc462e5c31da52395b697.jpg&h=e4b48687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係唔係太大火或者落得太多黑椒？</blockquote><br />\n幾好啊冇乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你依個靚好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"640367e568b070121721d19c370a3de32dbdb943","tid":247981,"uid":45917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大火煎封兩邊再轉小火煎，反密d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見到反密d...已經唔洗理"},{"pid":"faffae1cd16992e76bef5a11d0e588b614e84f41","tid":247981,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:38:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大火煎封兩邊再轉小火煎，反密d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見到反密d...已經唔洗理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有種煮法係咁喎"},{"pid":"27a1912db29782da1a139dbd90d052ca9e9bbad4","tid":247981,"uid":15336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:41:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>煮前有無拎出黎放30分鐘</blockquote><br />\n有喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n塊扒幾厚？<br />\n咁下gr個招 煎煎下放係garlic上面煮？<br />\n(我都未試個 佢好似煮腓力牛扒先咁做)<br />\n試下要細火d<br />\n每邊兩分鐘(最好只番一次面 之後煎條橫邊) 放10分鐘 食</blockquote><br />\n最好反密啲 封完兩邊之後 半分鐘就好反一次 甚至最密啲都唔過份<br />\n因為我地平時屋企用果啲平底鑊易潔鑊受熱溫度唔平均<br />\n如果你係用生鐵有坑紋果隻<br />\n就可以做只反一次<br />\n不過一般屋企冇需要買<br />\n因為買返黎真係淨係煎牛扒用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"771fb8d39d1b5d93461faf3e868cf9ae5346d44d","tid":247981,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"最緊要乾身<br />\n醬汁腌料調味唔好咁早落<br />\n油其實唔駛"},{"pid":"dfed9a44bef81809d56d73d6996cf879eb385401","tid":247981,"uid":100435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:59:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大火煎封兩邊再轉小火煎，反密d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見到反密d...已經唔洗理</blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>salt and pepper<br />\nolive oil in the pan<br />\nsteak, in<br />\nthyme, garlic<br />\na minute each side<br />\nflip once<br />\nbutter, in<br />\nget a spoon, start basting</blockquote><br />\n根本呢個就係完美示範, 只係個個當人講笑"},{"pid":"e097382c8305bb9f54e597e6354d2644de7943fc","tid":247981,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:01:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最緊要乾身<br />\n醬汁腌料調味唔好咁早落<br />\n油其實唔駛</blockquote><br />\n我知牛本身會出油 太真係一滴油都唔洗落落去個pan到?<br />\n唔洗燒紅個pan咩"},{"pid":"b5a4a91bfbbb50bff4e86f22ce9c015d82f2affd","tid":247981,"uid":100435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最緊要乾身<br />\n醬汁腌料調味唔好咁早落<br />\n油其實唔駛</blockquote><br />\n我知牛本身會出油 太真係一滴油都唔洗落落去個pan到?<br />\n唔洗燒紅個pan咩</blockquote><br />\n睇你咩牛, A5和牛 本身就係油, 仲洗乜落<br />\n普通冇咁肥既牛,唔落油 受熱唔平均"},{"pid":"ba