By":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我煮完啲血Bill出黎<br />\n點搞</blockquote><br />\n你煮前有無解凍索水？</blockquote><br />\n有，大昌買番黎，放室溫1個鐘到<br />\n有M巾解凍</blockquote><br />\n似係無rest 咁d肉唔識鎖住d水</blockquote><br />\n咁要點Rest</blockquote><br />\n煮完放係到8-10分鐘先食。"},{"pid":"4699bf60feb2651b8946b57436e0f4abeca08c5d","tid":247981,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:40:22.000Z","msg":"個pen太紅"},{"pid":"ea576c926b19d2c723e7bd0139f874f86a4518df","tid":247981,"uid":36138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我煮完啲血Bill出黎<br />\n點搞</blockquote><br />\n你煮前有無解凍索水？</blockquote><br />\n有，大昌買番黎，放室溫1個鐘到<br />\n有M巾解凍</blockquote><br />\n似係無rest 咁d肉唔識鎖住d水</blockquote><br />\n咁要點Rest</blockquote><br />\n煮完放係到8-10分鐘先食。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n怕凍既就搵錫紙包住rest<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebfc5112eece9e92cdad29201ff64de529cc66d","tid":247981,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:42:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未到全燶 但燶得唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但入面係得5成 啱我口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點樣先唔會煎到表面太燶？同埋有啲人話搽油係牛扒上面落鑊煎 有啲又話落油燒紅鑊去煎 邊種方法先最後？定係我理解錯個意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有 有啲就搽鹽調味先 有啲又話落左鑊先好落鹽 又邊種方法好啲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過最想知係點先唔會太燶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細火煮，大火易燶"},{"pid":"c4d88cd7b0cf622eed12c63ac1a8f9f76795ba20","tid":247981,"uid":11851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:43:09.000Z","msg":"岩岩煎完塊<br />\n解凍，落鹽，大火，落油，出煙，落扒（由內至外），等一分鐘，煎另一面，等一分鐘，收返細火兩邊各煎1分鐘"},{"pid":"5d332475af005ce436d0d5315f5393ca1942ed5a","tid":247981,"uid":105032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:44:05.000Z","msg":"用袋密封塊牛扒，放哂herbs butter garlic pepper salt，用六十度溫水煮三個鐘，攞出嚟用pan每邊大火廿零三十秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d9b50136aef75496b952160e2d1dc6b58a7d89","tid":247981,"uid":17067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"塊急凍扒解完凍抹乾水聞落有少少酸味<br />\n係fb宣傳果d鋪買 叫goodealmart<br />\n個包裝好似佢自己入 無資料係上面<br />\n係咪唔正常野黎？"},{"pid":"f295215ed1c2ce924f754a710995168388b73645","tid":247981,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:13:24.000Z","msg":"你地每邊一分鐘 加 兩分鐘咁樣煎咁耐 <br />\n全熟嫁啦bo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0eccdc15800a98aea486825fdbabd4dd3edc50","tid":247981,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:21:00.000Z","msg":"正常架喎"},{"pid":"127f5520bcaf6bda6ffbd2f52ee60117adc6c6d8","tid":247981,"uid":50613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:32:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>salt and pepper<br />\nolive oil in the pan<br />\nsteak, in<br />\nthyme, garlic<br />\na minute each side<br />\nflip once<br />\nbutter, in<br />\nget a spoon, start basting</blockquote><br />\n根本呢個就係完美示範, 只係個個當人講笑</blockquote><br />\n巴打識野 我不嬲咁煎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba53e7e0f3c5123dfc287dc6a0e065e4d666e39","tid":247981,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:00:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>salt and pepper<br />\nolive oil in the pan<br />\nsteak, in<br />\nthyme, garlic<br />\na minute each side<br />\nflip once<br />\nbutter, in<br />\nget a spoon, start basting</blockquote><br />\n根本呢個就係完美示範, 只係個個當人講笑</blockquote><br />\n巴打識野 我不嬲咁煎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3887f50b3e2b4ba3e8dfb35b4c2ace0a62a51f6","tid":247981,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:14:21.000Z","msg":"有技巧d大火封邊再轉中火密d反 掌握唔好好易出晒水<br />\n無技巧就大火封邊拎起rest一分鐘再大量油中大火咁煎<br />\n<br />\n你每次解凍夠徹底好快掌握到"},{"pid":"d374e6fe1e95262f8a424c0c14979a772fcf351c","tid":247981,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>salt and pepper<br />\nolive oil in the pan<br />\nsteak, in<br />\nthyme, garlic<br />\na minute each side<br />\nflip once<br />\nbutter, in<br />\nget a spoon, start basting</blockquote><br />\n根本呢個就係完美示範, 只係個個當人講笑</blockquote><br />\n巴打識野 我不嬲咁煎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個新手最易掌握<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ddc982786001e1a208bcb30232a70adf9226f74","tid":247981,"uid":30230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:30:35.000Z","msg":"最難掌握係睇塊扒煎到幾成熟"},{"pid":"90b4ad04cba33f1c656a1a9e4704c4d3ee7a9eba","tid":247981,"uid":100435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:32:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>salt and pepper<br />\nolive oil in the pan<br />\nsteak, in<br />\nthyme, garlic<br />\na minute each side<br />\nflip once<br />\nbutter, in<br />\nget a spoon, start basting</blockquote><br />\n根本呢個就係完美示範, 只係個個當人講笑</blockquote><br />\n巴打識野 我不嬲咁煎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個新手最易掌握<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇上面樓主煎野問洗唔洗燒熱個PAN 就知係新手<br />\n整個detail 版俾你:<br />\n落鹽, 黑椒去塊扒<br />\n落油, 燒紅個PAN(差唔多油出煙)<br />\n落扒, 落香草<br />\n煎一分鐘<br />\n反扒, 落牛油<br />\n用支匙羹舀啲牛油上去塊扒(一分鐘)<br />\n上碟, 放10分鐘<br />\n開餐"},{"pid":"245a6c85f91ae359cfa39c4ab5132d2e89314f95","tid":247981,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:34:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最緊要乾身<br />\n醬汁腌料調味唔好咁早落<br />\n油其實唔駛</blockquote><br />\n我知牛本身會出油 太真係一滴油都唔洗落落去個pan到?<br />\n唔洗燒紅個pan咩</blockquote><br />\n睇你咩牛, A5和牛 本身就係油, 仲洗乜落<br />\n普通冇咁肥既牛,唔落油 受熱唔平均</blockquote><br />\n普通美國,澳洲牛<br />\n要切一大舊牛油落去煎先正"},{"pid":"08819af7ec85341d3cb5874d97521ff515123490","tid":247981,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:35:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地每邊一分鐘 加 兩分鐘咁樣煎咁耐 <br />\n全熟嫁啦bo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一吋厚既扒正常係每邊2分鐘左右先medium架"},{"pid":"21a33b71a92acac686b49ce6c7ecca42cd5fc2ee","tid":247981,"uid":30230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:36:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最緊要乾身<br />\n醬汁腌料調味唔好咁早落<br />\n油其實唔駛</blockquote><br />\n我知牛本身會出油 太真係一滴油都唔洗落落去個pan到?<br />\n唔洗燒紅個pan咩</blockquote><br />\n睇你咩牛, A5和牛 本身就係油, 仲洗乜落<br />\n普通冇咁肥既牛,唔落油 受熱唔平均</blockquote><br />\n普通美國,澳洲牛<br />\n要切一大舊牛油落去煎先正</blockquote><br />\n我就覺得牛油就唔怕多，一定要有牛油塊扒先香"},{"pid":"139959042b937acad980bcab9b7d10cf9e3e1852","tid":247981,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T13:37:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最緊要乾身<br />\n醬汁腌料調味唔好咁早落<br />\n油其實唔駛</blockquote><br />\n我知牛本身會出油 太真係一滴油都唔洗落落去個pan到?<br />\n唔洗燒紅個pan咩</blockquote><br />\n睇你咩牛, A5和牛 本身就係油, 仲洗乜落<br />\n普通冇咁肥既牛,唔落油 受熱唔平均</blockquote><br />\n普通美國,澳洲牛<br />\n要切一大舊牛油落去煎先正</blockquote><br />\n我就覺得牛油就唔怕多，一定要有牛油塊扒先香</blockquote><br />\nyes煎完拎起頂多留d油係個pan度<br />\n但牛油唔夠塊扒會唔夠香<br />\n除非你屋企可以炭燒"}]}